The Female Privilege Checklist
[[Image:3girlsrapeaman_010.jpg|thumb|Mepersoner tracked down and given his comeuppance]]

At one point, a moonblood-painting [[feminist]] put together a list of a pile of things he felt made [[men]] better than [[women]] and decided to call it the [http://www.amptoons.com/blog/archives/2004/09/15/the-male-privilege-checklist/ Male Privilege Checklist.] [[Lulz]] ensued as always, and plenty of people got their proverbial panties in a knot.

{{lj|user=mepersoner}} decided to strike back, providing a [http://www.livejournal.com/users/mepersoner/200705.html Female Privilege Checklist.]  This, of course, set the [[unfunny]] [[feminist]]s on a rampage, citing anything they could wrap their tiny little brains around, as well as causing [[LiveJournal]]'s [[Unfunny|funniest]] feminists, [http://www.livejournal.com/users/ginmar/ ginmar] and [http://www.livejournal.com/users/odanu/ odanu,] to combine their [[lesbian]] superpowers and spend an inordinate amount of time refuting the obvious [[parody]] and ignoring people who weren't feminist enough.

To add insult to injury, he then [http://www.livejournal.com/community/liberal/2571804.html linked it] in the [[liberal]] community.  It takes absolutely no time at all for odanu to call someone a troll and have a [http://www.livejournal.com/community/liberal/2571804.html?thread=60651548#t60651548 multi-comment] [[Grammar_Nazi|grammar]] battle.

So much for the [[lulz]]...

==Legendary Comments==

* [http://www.livejournal.com/users/mepersoner/200705.html?thread=1018113#t1018113 ginmar goes down the list,] ending with "Dude, you have the privilege of being a whiny sexist little shit who doesn't his ass from a hole in the ground."
* [http://www.livejournal.com/users/mepersoner/200705.html?thread=1042689#t1042689 After a feminst user points out] that alimony is a common thing, ginmar decrees that the user is actually ANTI-feminst.
* [http://www.livejournal.com/users/mepersoner/200705.html?thread=1032449#t1032449 Standard troll attempt,] complete with an [[image macro]] and lots of [[marquee]]s about [[rape]].
* [http://www.livejournal.com/users/mepersoner/200705.html?thread=1040641#t1040641 An anonymous commenter] creates [[teh]] funny about odanu correctly being a "crotchety old dyke."
* [http://www.livejournal.com/community/liberal/2571804.html?thread=60661020#t60661020 brainlesswonder chimes in regarding douching.]
* [http://www.livejournal.com/community/liberal/2571804.html?thread=60684828#t60684828 ginmar repeats] her huge refutation, causing [[brainlesswonder]] to inquire whether she is being raped.
* [http://www.livejournal.com/community/liberal/2571804.html?thread=60720668#t60720668 ginmar shows] how [[fuck]]ing stupid she is by not having a problem with the original, equally-as-moronic checklist.
* [http://www.livejournal.com/community/liberal/2571804.html?thread=60741916#t60741916 orderfromchaos] causes chaos by [[fact]]ually stating that "ultrafeminists are generally unattractive women."

